CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 8 reads: "Thousands Attend Courier Home, Food Show...10. Supreme Liberty Life Insurance Company passed out souvenirs to both children and grown-ups. Shown here are local representatives, Mrs. Rozelia Jarrison, Miss Marie Coleman, Howard Robers and Oscar Jones..Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Rozelia Jarrison, Marie Coleman, Howard Roberts, and Oscar Jones seated in Supreme Life Insurance Company booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
